text: Quiet park on a Sunday late afternoon. 3 bus options at the bus stop along the road. Very basic playground so nothing worth mentioning. That said, there is a plot of land that had a sign "listed for sale" by URA. Might be interesting to follow subsequent  developments in this area
Playground is nice and clean. It is a small park with a small playground and some basic exercise equipment.
Peaceful and relaxing. I used to visit this place often after work, it was just a 5 min walk away from my place.
a minimalist playground located in a residential area. A suitable place for relaxing with small children and an open gym for those who want to maintain fitness
Kids friendly. Good playground. Slides, spring-type sea saw and a merry go round. Beginner running track for joggers; no slope or tough terrain for the avid runners. Can scoot around TOP.
